    "multicolumn_qfbi3h": {
      "type": "multicolumn",
      "blocks": {
        "column_UiEc4N": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "title": "",
            "text": "<p>The P62 features the HED Vanquish V62 rim platform, utilizing one of the most aerodynamically optimized rim profiles on the market. Handcrafted in Minnesota, the P62 inherits HED’s legacy of world-class performance. With drag numbers as low as negative 100g, these wheels minimize aerodynamic drag like no other, delivering some of the fastest, smoothest rides available.<br/><br/>With a 62mm depth and 22.4mm internal width and hooked bead, P62 Carbon Aero wheels can run tires from 28 to 55c and at pressures of up to 75 psi. (25c tires)</p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": ""
          }
        },
        "column_PyBEd9": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "title": "",
            "text": "<p>At the core of the P62 wheels are Berd Polylight spokes—the lightest bicycle spokes in the world. Made from a unique polymer composite, these spokes provide exceptional strength-to-weight ratio while offering inherent vibration damping properties. The result is a wheel that’s not only lighter but delivers a noticeably smoother ride. The added flexibility of the Berd spokes ensures that the typically harsh ride characteristics of deep-section aerodynamic rims are mitigated, delivering comfort without sacrificing performance.</p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": ""
          }
        },
        "column_iGpqfX": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "title": "",
            "text": "<p>Berd P62 wheels come built around our flagship Berd Talon Road hubs, along with black Industry Nine Solix Centerlock hubs. For a truly unique wheelset, choose Onyx Vesper Hook Flange hubs. The result is a fully Minnesota-made wheelset. These hubs, along with Berd and HED’s engineering, deliver a truly exceptional product that’s assembled within 60 miles of each other—representing the best of local manufacturing. . Please allow up to 4-6 weeks for delivery of Onyx Vesper Hook Flange wheels.</p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": ""
          }
        }
      },
