            "title": "<strong>Dampening</strong>",
            "text": "<p>Berd spokes provide 200% better vibration damping than metal spokes. Berd spokes provide an unparalleled smooth riding experience that is unobtainable with conventional spokes, at no expense to power transfer when you need it most. Ride further and faster with less fatigue.</p>",
